# Code Style Rules

## Python

- Line length: 88 (Match black formatter)
- Quotes: Double quotes for strings
- Docstring: Google style
- Imports:
  - Order: stdlib, third_party, first_party, local
  - Group by type: true
  - Banned: 
    - "from .. import *" (No relative imports)
    - "import *" (No wildcard imports)
- Indent:
  - Style: space
  - Size: 4

## TypeScript

- Quotes: single
- Semicolons: required
- Indent: 2 spaces
